linux-source-3.18.13-5-ev3dev-rpi (1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add device tree override for Raspberry Pi LED labels.
  * Add Dexter Industries BrickPi device tree overlay.
  * Include device tree dtb files in package.
  * Merge upstream kernel 3.18.13.
  * Change CONFIG_HZ to 1000.

  [lego-linux-drivers]
  * Change LED names. Now all ev3dev LEDs always end with ":ev3dev".
  * I2C drivers now work on any I2C adapter.
  * Add support for Dexter Industries BrickPi.
  * Add "ev3:" prefix to EV3 input and output port names.

